A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Part 1 of Article 2 of Chapter 8 of Title 12 of the Official Code of Georgia
2 Annotated, relating to general provisions relative to solid waste management, so as to require
3 the recycling of solar panels; to prohibit the discarding or disposing of solar panels by any
4 manner other than by delivery to a collection or recovered materials processing facility or
5 other recycling center that accepts solar panels for recycling; to provide for definitions; to
6 provide for penalties; to provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other
7 purposes.
8 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
9 SECTION 1.
10 Part 1 of Article 2 of Chapter 8 of Title 12 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
11 relating to general provisions relative to solid waste management, is amended by adding a
12 new Code section to read as follows:
13 "12-8-28.1.
14 (a) As used in this Code section, the term:
15 (1) 'Solar panel' means any device that contains a bank of solar cells or other solar energy
16 collection system that when exposed to solar radiation can generate electricity.
